e gains in terms of operating range of wireless power transfer (WPT),\ntotal harvested energy, as well as achievable rate can be obtained by our\nproposed designs over benchmark schemes (especially the one adopting a passive\nIRS). Moreover, it is advisable to deploy an active IRS in the proximity of the\nusers for the effective operation of WPT/SWIPT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 06:46:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 07:37:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-05"}
