efully calibrated aperture mass\nfunction emulator, cluster cosmology analyses can use cluster aperture masses\ndirectly, reducing the sensitivity to model-dependent mass calibration biases\nand uncertainties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 14:59:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2022 17:12:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
